      .row.align-items-center
        .col-md-5.order-0.order-md-1.text-end
          img.pt-7.pt-md-0.w-100(src=`${CWD}assets/img/gallery/hero.png` alt='hero-header')
        .col-md-7.text-md-start.text-center.py-8
          h1.fw-normal.fs-6.fs-xl-7.mb-2 A trusted provider of 
            br
            .fw-bolder courier services.
          p.fs-1.mb-5 We deliver your products safely to 
            br
            |your home in a reasonable time.  
          a.btn.btn-primary.me-2(href='#!' role='button') Get started
            i.fas.fa-arrow-right.ms-2